courses.learning_outcomes:
Upon completion of this course, students will be able to:
1. Understand the history and evolution of Chinese characters;
2. Understand the formation of Chinese characters;
3. Read individual words and short phrases in real life contexts;
4. Notice the use of traditional Chinese characters and simplified Chinese characters in the Greater Bay Area.

完成本科目後，學生將能夠：
1. 了解漢字的歷史和演變;
2. 了解漢字的構造;
3. 閱讀現實生活中的單詞和短語;
4. 注意大灣區使用繁體字和簡體字的情況。

Upon completion of this course, students will be able to:
1. Produce Cantonese sounds accurately;
2. Identify phonetic rules and apply them to pronunciation properly;
3. Reduce pronunciation errors;
4. Identify meaning-change through tones;
5. Speak accurately and fluently.

完成本科目後，學生將能夠：
1. 準確地發出廣東話聲音；
2. 識別語音規則並將其應用到説話中；
3. 減少發音錯誤；
4. 通過不同聲調識別意義變化；
5. 說話準確流利。

Upon completion of this course, students will be able to:
1. Engage and participate in oral discussion on cultural topics;
2. Gain the cultural knowledge and vocabulary on Cantonese culture;
3. Improve accuracy in Cantonese pronunciation;
4. Improve the ability to understand Cantonese and to reuse them.

完成本科目後，學生將能夠：
1. 參與文化話題的口頭討論；
2. 掌握廣東文化知識和詞彙；
3. 提高粵語發音的準確性；
4. 提高理解粤语和重複使用粵語的能力。
